1:12:24.006 --> 1:12:26.918
Rob: Our lead plaintiff
is Mr. Joe kiger.

1:12:27.009 --> 1:12:30.593
Potential plaintiff,
if the partnership approves.

1:12:30.680 --> 1:12:33.012
Mr. Joe kiger, a phys ed teacher

1:12:33.099 --> 1:12:35.215
from parkersburg, West Virginia.

1:12:35.309 --> 1:12:39.803
On behalf of
the 70,000 local residents,

1:12:39.897 --> 1:12:42.764
whose water
dupont knowingly poisoned

1:12:42.859 --> 1:12:44.190
