that dupont had found

1:12:51.868 --> 1:12:55.656
small concentrations of c-8
in their water supply,

1:12:55.746 --> 1:12:57.202
but not to worry

1:12:57.290 --> 1:13:00.657
because those concentrations
were safe.

1:13:00.751 --> 1:13:03.663
